T02D2343:2b-1: bi ka wa pa ri ha ra sti ka n'a ma /
T02D2343:2b-3: rnam rtog spang ba'i glu zhes bya ba /
T02D2343:2b-4: dpal ha ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2343:2b-5: po la gsang ba'i rdo rje la //
T02D2343:2b-6: 'dus pa sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
T02D2343:2b-7: thig le gsang ba'i rtsa la breng //
T02D2343:2b-8: kakko la yi kha sbyor la //
T02D2343:2b-9: kye ho re ni 'bar bar byed //
T02D2343:2b-10: kri bi ta yi sgra sgrogs pas //
T02D2343:2b-11: rtsa drug 'khor lo h'um gis bcing //
T02D2343:2b-12: sku gsum dh'u t'ir bdag med rtogs //
T02D2343:2b-13: rang byung me tog ldan pa yi //
T02D2343:2b-14: ga pur po la bsres byas nas //
T02D2343:2b-15: ka ru ka'i bdud rtsi 'thung bar gyis //
T02D2343:2b-16: ka li dze ra skal bar ldan //
T02D2343:2b-17: rnal 'byor tshogs su bsre bar bya //
T02D2343:2b-18: 'du dhu ra skal bar mi ldan te //
T02D2343:2b-19: spongs shig rnal 'byor dam tshig go //
T02D2343:2b-20: bzhi mnyam gla rtsi lus byugs nas //
T02D2343:2b-21: rtog pa rnams ni spang bar bya ;
T02D2343:2b-22: / dpa' bo dpa' mo'i tshogs dag tu //
T02D2343:2b-23: he ru ka yi nga rgyal ldan //
T02D2343:2b-24: sha wa zhing chen khur byas nas //
T02D2343:2b-25: ma la rigs skyes dra ma zel //
T02D2343:2b-26: kun du phrad pa'i rnal 'byor ba //
T02D2343:2b-27: rtog pa mi bya lus la gnas //
T02D2343:2b-28: kye ho skal ldan mchod par gyis //
T02D2343:2b-29: li la bdag med seng ge yis //
T02D2343:2b-30: stong nyid don ni rtogs par 'gyur //
T02D2343:2b-31: rnam rtog spang phyir rnal 'byor kye //
T02D2343:2b-32: bdag ni gan rgyal nyal byas nas //
T02D2343:2b-33: lag pa bsnol nas bral la sbyar //
T02D2343:2b-34: rang rig nam mkha'i phyogs su gtad //
T02D2343:2b-35: li la skyes te gnyis med rtogs //
T02D2343:2b-36: rtog med rnal 'byor grub pa thob //
T02D2343:2b-37: li la pa yis rtogs nas gol //
